{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":9,"day":22}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"欢呼革命大联合〔数来宝〕","authors":["峭岩佩琈金宝"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛泽东思想红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命大批判掀高潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：毛泽东思想闪金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命左派斗志昂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛泽东思想是根本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命形势好得很。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：毛泽东思想照山河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派实现了大联"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：大联合，实在好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那报喜的队伍有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队队，一排排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩荡荡走过来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席像，语录牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大红喜字肩上抬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗舞，锣鼓敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘹亮歌声冲云霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）“大海航行靠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万物生长靠太阳…"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）你咋这么激动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（白）激动？激动的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在后头呢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是说，又是笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是蹦，又是跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又握手，又拥抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有人嘀嘀哒哒把泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）嗯，是够激动的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：革命派实现了大联"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说快活不快活？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）快活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：革命派团结齐上阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说带劲不带劲？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）带劲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：革命派紧跟毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说可喜不可喜？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）可喜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：革命派思想革命化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说可怕不可怕？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）可怕……不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，我不怕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你不怕，有人怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资本主义道路当权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派一见头发炸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派联合力量大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火力集中对准他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷追猛打把根挖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说他害怕不害怕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：大联合，是方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结战斗有力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：联合起来有气魄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能斗倒走资本主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路当权派！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：联合起来雄赳赳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能埋葬封、资、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（白）呵！封、资、修？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）就是封建主"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义、资本主义、修正"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：联合起来势如海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能完成斗、批、改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：联合起来力无比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能把文化大革命进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：大联合，大联合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报频传遍全国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级打头炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命大联合起风暴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红流滚滚赛长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天翻地覆慨而慷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：这真是千条小河归大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那革命大军多豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命形势实在好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠毛主席来领导！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）毛主席说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“在工人阶级内部，没有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根本的利害冲突。在无产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级专政下的工人阶级内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部，更没有理由一定要分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裂成为势不两立的两大派"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛主席，一声令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军万马齐行动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：大联合号角震天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派红心向太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：破私心，削“山头”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派紧跟毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做什么“张家派”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“李家派”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心要做毛泽东思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：千条小河汇大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命洪流滚滚来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结在毛泽东思想红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命力量比天大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：革命大联合实在好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级敌人吓坏了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮阴风，放暗箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千方百计要捣乱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴一套，阳一套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想把大联合来搞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：呸！办不到，办不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有毛泽东思想来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派，看得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破除恶浪扫妖风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：大联合，大批判，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席咋说咱咋办。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大批判，大联合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席咋说咱咋做。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：握紧枪，攥紧笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓把革命干到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛主席，挥巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派乘风破浪大步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：毛主席，指方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派刀山火海也敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：革命派永远跟着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海枯石烂心不移！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派永远跟着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百战百胜永无敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席万岁！万万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁！万岁！毛主席！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}